320
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:17,300
Is it over?

321
00:18:19,950 --> 00:18:20,650
Madam.

322
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:23,360
What did you do today?

323
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:25,690
