Everything will be fine.

393
00:22:24,710 --> 00:22:25,390
I'll stay here.

394
00:22:25,390 --> 00:22:26,230
You go in first.

395
00:22:26,230 --> 00:22:26,830
Go.

396
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:27,710
