421
00:23:50,390 --> 00:23:51,310
One year ago,

422
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:52,670
I sent

423
00:23:53,170 --> 00:23:55,800
five trusted subordinates

424
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,830
into the heart of danger.

425
00:23:58,710 --> 00:24:00,750
