426
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:02,590
It was thanks to you two

427
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:04,710
that my men's bodies were recovered.

428
00:24:06,050 --> 00:24:06,920
This year,

429
00:24:07,510 --> 00:24:09,170
I dreamed of them every night.

430
