452
00:25:29,150 --> 00:25:29,870
Right?

453
00:25:31,830 --> 00:25:32,990
Mr. Moqi?

454
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:43,270
Or should I call you

455
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,020
Ms. Moqi?

456
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:13,430
[Moqi]

457
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:23,400
