533
00:29:33,230 --> 00:29:36,310
I sent someone to watch your pleasure boat.

534
00:29:36,710 --> 00:29:37,830
They said

535
00:29:38,150 --> 00:29:39,230
your attendant

536
00:29:40,260 --> 00:29:41,790
