554
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:11,500
We don't have to leave.

555
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,490
We just need to arrest you.

556
00:32:30,870 --> 00:32:32,660
How dare you try to

557
00:32:32,870 --> 00:32:34,870
